{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2299d83fb5","title":"中央转发河南省委关于农业合作化问题的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"48fb30cc6b","index":0,"year":1955,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"2299d83fb5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b6f582eb02","type":"title","text":"中央转发河南省委关于农业合作化问题的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"4ae6c570ab","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"4947041b1e","type":"appellation","text":"上海局、各省市委、自治区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"583aa491b9","type":"paragraph","text":"现将河南省委八月二十八日关于农业合作化问题的报告一件，发给你们参考。中央认为河南省委的方针是正确的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"f113f6ffd3","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央一九五五年九月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2299d83fb5"}],"page":{"id":"9c7bebfc9b","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2299d83fb5","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"1219419c04","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央副秘书长、中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"558c946250","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。伯达，即陈伯达，当时任中共中央农村工作部副部长。"},{"id":"8948026934","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。朱，指朱德。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"c27c452f81","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共河南省委在报告中说，省委于1955年8月16日至22日召开了扩大会议，传达讨论了毛泽东《关于农业合作化问题》的指示，联系省委指导思想和实际工作的问题，开展了批评与自我批评，进一步明确了对合作化运动的指导思想和对合作社全面规划加强领导的方针；通过了全省发展农业合作社的指标：即在今冬明春发展到10万个社，使入社农户达到总农户数的30%，1957年年底以前发展到18万个，入社农户达到总农户数的60%以上。会议还强调当前整顿现有农业合作社的重要性，并部署在今年9月、10月间第二次整顿，明年春夏第三次整顿。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1219419c04","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年九月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"47a8382083","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"4f2de64b1d","type":"title","text":"中央转发河南省委关于农业合作化问题的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"558c946250","type":"paragraph","text":"现将河南省委八月二十八日关于农业合作化问题的报告“一件，发给你们参考。中央认为河南省委的方针是正确的","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"5e217a4202","type":"paragraph","text":"九月四日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"8948026934","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"9cd87b0b46","type":"paragraph","text":"周、伯达阅后，即送刘朱陈邓阅，尚昆以用电报即发，另印如前示。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"},{"id":"c27c452f81","type":"paragraph","text":"上海局、各省市委、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5"}],"page":{"id":"40aad97fe7","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"2299d83fb5","start":333,"end":334}}}},"__N_SSG":true}